She looked at Black Aracnia.  "I'm going." she lowered her head and 
walked in.
"I am here to join you and the other preds.  You have my commander.  
This I understand and will not do anything that will put him in 
jeopardy. I know that your group is far superior to that of 
Megatron's. I simply wish to serve the strongest group possible."
She needed to see Quickstrike to figure out what needed to be done. 
No matter what, her loyalty was to Quickstrike.
